1.2
log
@observe the following spelling:
- wide character (noun)
- wide-character (adjective)

this is the "fix of least resistance", and appears to be in line with
posix style; a tiny fix still needed for curses, but i'll mail that
upstream;
@
text
@.\" $OpenBSD: wcstod.3,v 1.1 2009/01/13 18:44:01 kettenis Exp $
.\" $NetBSD: wcstod.3,v 1.5 2007/05/21 15:29:51 tnozaki Exp $
